<td sourcefile="commerce/product-recommendations.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">AI-ML</td>
<td sourcefile="commerce/product-recommendations.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">This module recommends a personalized list of products based on purchase patterns of the signed-in user. For a guest user, this list will be collapsed.</td>
</tr>
